(100, 1, '2015-10-12 22:40:40', '2015-10-12 22:40:40', 'Cécile Klingler is a Freelance health and science journalist. Prior to this, she worked as a biology Editor and staff writer at the French science magazine La Recherche for 14 years. At La Recherche she covered a broad range of science and health topics, including infectious diseases. She later worked as the news editor at the magazine, and ran a column on environmental and bioethics.\r\n\r\nsteering committee ', 'Cécile Klingler', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cecile-klingler', '', '', '2015-10-12 22:40:40', '2015-10-12 22:40:40', '', 0, 'http://localhost/~mpierre1/projects/clients/WFSJ/?p=100', 0, 'post', '', 0),
